sc_cat_item.description: The Cyber Cat: Universal Headphone Holder is a stylish and functional 3D printable accessory for headphone storage. Its unique cybernetic cat design adds a touch of futuristic flair to any desk or workspace, while securely holding a wide variety of headphones. Keep your headphones organized and on display with this cool and quirky holder.
sc_cat_item.name: Cyber Cat: Universal Headphone Holder
